
** Commands

<pre>
<verbatim>

RMAN> startup;
RMAN> shutdown;

-- backup
RMAN> backup database;
RMAN> backup incremental level 1 database;

-- backup tablespace
RMAN> bakup tablespace system;

-- backup archive logs
RMAN> backup archivelog all delete input;

-- verify
RMAN> restore database validate;

-- restore
RMAN> restore database;
RMAN> recover database;
RMAN> alter database open;

-- restore tablespace
RMAN> SQL 'alter tablespace tools offline immediate';
RMAN> restore tablespace tools;
RMAN> SQL 'alter tablespace tools online';

-- list
RMAN> reoport schema;
RMAN> list backup;
RMAN> list backup summary;
RMAN> list copy;

-- show
RMAN> show all;

-- delete
RMAN> delete backupset 231;
RMAN> delete backup TAG='TAG20030823T181616';

-- change
RMAN> change backupset 231 nokeep;

</verbatim>
</pre>

** Channel Switching

<pre>
<verbatim>

RMAN> run {
allocate channel c1 device type sbt;
backup current controlfile;
}

</verbatim>
</pre>

** Configure

<pre>
<verbatim>

RMAN> configure device type sbt clear;

</verbatim>
</pre>


